reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sweet upgrade! Quick!
reviews.reviewText: Sweet upgrade! Very Quick! It did not work on my Lenovo 11e, but found out later that for that laptop an adapter was necessary. Installed on another laptop (Acer Nitro) that uses a standard size 2280 NVME SSD. Needed to adapt it for larger SSD carrier, but works great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Installed as an upgrade from a 128GB SSD to this 1TB on a 4 yr old Asus laptop. It was easy to do and this upgraded SSD works perfectly and solved a critical space problem on my C: drive. It was an easy DIY project with a little help from YouTube research. Saved me from having to buy a new laptop!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars For Portable Computer
reviews.reviewText: Originally my hard drive was 16 GB for a chrome box. Changed the OS to Windows 10 Pro. I upgraded to 32 GB SSD drive. I didn’t have enough space so it was slowing my computer down and I bought this 256 GB SSD drive. It was very affordable and for a name brand. I don’t want to buy a Chinese brand where it might fail and you lose everything. I haven’t tested the speed but it’s fast and works with no issues. I got only 239 GB even though it stated 256 GB on package. I suspect they meant bytes as seen in my first photo. I have no regrets purchasing this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great customer service
reviews.reviewText: My drive went out just a couple of weeks before the one-year anniversary of the purchase. I contacted customer support, and they were very helpful and polite about the issue. They quickly sent out a replacement drive, which I received very quickly, and I returned the defective drive.The drive itself has performed great for my needs as a cache drive for a server. Easy to install and set up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Dead after 8 months
reviews.reviewText: Looked decent enough for the price and the reviews looked good enough when I bought it. I got this in late January and it worked well enough in my laptop for a couple months. In the middle of summer, though, it started displaying odd behavior, like randomly taking ages to load regular applications like Firefox. By the end of August, it became worse and worse to the point where it took 5 minutes to boot and even locked up my laptop in the middle of class. Unacceptable, even if cheap. Avoid.[The below is an addendum after going through the RMA process]RMA process went smoothly - you'll want to go through their email from your personal inbox rather than their website, though, if you want a faster reply. Emailing them directly got me a response in less than two days, going through their website took until I sent the SSD back to the first response.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Upgraded HP Envy lLaptop
reviews.reviewText: The laptop had a 256gb dual slot M.2 drive in it. I upgraded it to 512. The clone worked great.
Computer would not recognize drive on motherboard slot, worked fine as a USB attached drive. Returned wit no problems and full refund. 5 * for customer responsiveness.

O produto vem conforme o anúncio. Entretanto se trata de um serviço de intermediário de compra internacional (da China/hong Kong), informação omitida na descrição do anúncio. O prazo de envio foi moroso, além de ter ocorrido extravio na primeira encomenda. Não compensou pelo tempo de espera.
Chegou a tempo e foi a melhor compra de 2021
